{"tid":2002024,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【新盤部署】康城Malibu一房折實8球 兩年貴43%","createTime":"2020-05-05T03:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T10:14:56.000Z","uid":160028,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"84a8cfe2862f60207ea6f4946ffe3bc3a71a99c4","tid":2002024,"uid":160028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:21:24.000Z","msg":"樓市轉旺，新盤趁勢加推搶客。會德豐（020）將軍澳日出康城Malibu加推10伙單位，當中九伙屬連平台及天台特色戶，售價1,009.5萬至2,118.7萬元，呎價21,633元至27,432元，平均呎價23,172元。扣除最高20.5%折扣後，折實售價802.6萬至1,684.4萬元，呎價17,198元至21,810元，平均呎價18,423元。<br />\n<br />\n當中呎價最貴為3B座38樓E室一房單位，實用面積368方呎，定價1,009.5萬元，折實後仍要802.6萬元，呎價21,810元。價單顯示，凡購買該單位的買家，將可免費獲贈指明傢俱和物品，包括茶壺、托盤、書、地毯、藝術掛畫及碗等，詳情可參考價單。有關傢俱及物件將於該單位成交日以「現狀」及「屆時之現狀」交予買方。對比舊價單，樓下一層3B座37樓E室，實用面積同為368方呎，2018年1月定價713.3萬元，單位最終折實以560萬元成交，呎價15,217元。今次加推單位只高一層，樓價卻貴242.6萬元，意味加幅43%。<br />\n發展商同步上載銷售安排，落實於‪本周六（‪5月9日‬）上午11時發售。今天亦以招標形式推售餘下可供發售之單位6伙，包括2伙天台特色戶、4伙4房雙套，全屬優質海景單位，將於8月15日截<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200504/7H5MALDZ4E3TIV32VAI5ETU2OA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200504%2F7H5MALDZ4E3TIV32VAI5ETU2OA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=4447bddc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200504%2F7H5MALDZ4E3TIV32VAI5ETU2OA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=75988281\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200504/7H5MALDZ4E3TIV32VAI5ETU2OA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"2e3288d4617e361483ee222a9f3d9ef86b38495b","tid":200202